OL,7,FThe report found Mr Lyons had breached
OL,8,Fthe ministerial code of conduct
OL,9,Fthrough social media comments made
OL,10,Fduring rioting in Ballymena.
OL,12,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,13,Fhere.
OL,15,FHe was investigated over a Facebook
OL,16,Fpost he published in June after
OL,17,Fimmigrant families were forced to flee
OL,18,Ftheir homes during racially-motivated
OL,19,Friots.
