OL,7,FMr Lyons has said he had been
OL,8,Fresponding to a police request to let
OL,9,Fit be known that the fleeing families
OL,10,Fwho had been sheltering at Larne
OL,11,FLeisure Centre were no longer doing
OL,12,Fso, as the facility came under attack.
OL,14,FBut Ms McCullough's report found Mr
OL,15,FLyons' actions had the potential of
OL,16,F"heightening tensions and exacerbating
OL,17,Fan already contentious situation".
