OL,7,FMr Lyons has claimed that the report
OL,8,Fcontains contradictions, while DUP
OL,9,Fleader Gavin Robinson described the
OL,10,Ffindings as "totally irrational".
OL,12,FIn the Assembly on Tuesday, Opposition
OL,13,Fleader Matthew O'Toole said this had
OL,14,Fbeen the second occasion that Mr Lyons
OL,15,Fhad been found to be in breach of the
OL,16,Fministerial code.
