OL,7,FThis referred to a finding in 2024
OL,8,Fthat Mr Lyons had breached the code
OL,9,Fover not attending north-south
OL,10,Fministerial council meetings. That
OL,11,Fcame as part of a wider DUP boycott in
OL,12,Fprotest at post-Brexit arrangements.
OL,14,FMr O'Toole said as a result of "this
OL,15,Frepeated failure to uphold the
OL,16,Fstandards expected of public office
OL,17,Fholders", the minister "no longer
OL,18,Fcommands the confidence of this
OL,19,FAssembly".
