OL,7,F"Not only has the minister not
OL,8,Fresigned, the minister has not seen
OL,9,Ffit to apologise or even offer one
OL,10,Fword of reflection or learning," he
OL,11,Ftold MLAs.
OL,13,FThe motion also said Mr Lyons'
OL,14,F"refusal to accept responsibility for
OL,15,Fhis actions represents a wider crisis
OL,16,Fof accountability in the Executive and
OL,17,Fa deeper cultural problem in our
OL,18,Fpolitics", and that current
OL,19,Faccountability standards are
OL,20,F"inadequate".
