OL,7,FIt added that the Assembly would write
OL,8,Fto both Northern Ireland Secretary
OL,9,FHilary Benn and Tanaiste Simon Harris
OL,10,Fcalling for institutional reform at
OL,11,FStormont.
OL,13,FThe Assembly saw some stormy
OL,14,Fexchanges, accusations of lack of
OL,15,Fempathy with those impacted by the
OL,16,Friots in Ballymena as well as
OL,17,Fpolitical posturing.
