OL,7,FSinn Fein MLA Colm Gildernew described
OL,8,Fa "poorly judged Facebook post", which
OL,9,Fhe claimed "at no point in his post
OL,10,Fdid the minister show any compassion
OL,11,Ffor the victims of this hate-filled
OL,12,Fviolence".
OL,14,FHe also pointed out that the
OL,15,FCommunities committee, which he
OL,16,Fchairs, previously voted they had no
OL,17,Fconfidence in the minister.
OL,19,F"That position has been fully
OL,20,Fvindicated," he added.
