OL,7,FAlliance deputy leader Eoin Tennyson
OL,8,Fdescribed the rioting last June as a
OL,9,F"festival of violence" and a "race-
OL,10,Fbased pogrom on our streets", adding
OL,11,Fhe "took great exception to those
OL,12,Fclaiming this is a trivial matter".
OL,14,F"I am sick, sore and tired of Members
OL,15,Ftraipsing into this chamber and
OL,16,Fengaging in culture wars, and
OL,17,Fscapegoating minorities for their
OL,18,Ffailures," he said.
