OL,7,FUUP leader Jon Burrows queried the
OL,8,Fusage of resources on the matter of a
OL,9,F"Facebook post sent at the request of
OL,10,Fpolice".
OL,12,F"Could it have been drafted better,
OL,13,Fcould it have been more precise, is
OL,14,Fthere any learning? I'm sure there
OL,15,Fis," he told MLAs.
OL,17,F"There are many things for us to do in
OL,18,Fthis place, and drive up high
OL,19,Fstandards is one of them, but this is
OL,20,Fwasteful, self-indulgent and
OL,21,Funnecessary."
